~$ git clone git://github.com/ignovak/vimrc ~/.vim
~$ echo 'so ~/.vim/.vimrc' > ~/.vimrc
~$ cd ~/.vim
~/.vim$ git submodule init
~/.vim$ git submodule update

Inconsolata font: http://levien.com/type/myfonts/inconsolata.html

adding submodules:
~$ git submodule add git://github.com/hacker/vim-hacker.git ~/.vim/bundle/hacker
